<title>UK: UK construction orders fall 5% in 3 mths to March.</title>
<headline>UK construction orders fall 5% in 3 mths to March.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>UK new construction orders were 5.0 percent lower in the three months to March versus the previous three months, the Department of Environment said on Thursday.</p>
<p>The total volume of new orders received by contractors for construction work was also 5.0 percent lower quarter on quarter but was 6.0 percent higher than in the first quarter last year.</p>
<p>-- Michael Peacock, London newsroom +44 171 542 7708</p>
